### Backup (sistema unificado)

- `src/modules/backup/domain/entities/BackupSnapshot.ts` - entidades: `BackupSnapshot`, `BackupPayload` (con `images`, `suppliers`), `BackupTrigger`
- `src/modules/backup/domain/repositories/BackupRepository.ts` - interfaz
- `src/modules/backup/domain/repositories/ChangeTrackerPort.ts` - interfaz
- `src/modules/backup/infrastructure/repositories/SQLiteBackupRepository.ts` - repositorio SQLite
- `src/modules/backup/infrastructure/services/AutoBackupService.ts` - auto-backup, monitoreo, pre-eliminacion
- `src/modules/backup/infrastructure/services/ChangeDetector.ts` - deteccion de cambios
- `src/modules/backup/infrastructure/services/BackupImageCollector.ts` - coleccion y restauracion de imagenes
- `src/modules/backup/infrastructure/services/FileImportService.ts` - importar JSON legacy
- `src/modules/backup/application/use-cases/CreateBackupUseCase.ts` - crear backup con imagenes + suppliers
- `src/modules/backup/application/use-cases/RestoreBackupUseCase.ts` - restaurar backup con imagenes + suppliers
- `src/modules/backup/application/use-cases/ListBackupsUseCase.ts` - listar backups
- `src/modules/backup/application/dtos/BackupDtos.ts` - schemas Zod
- `src/modules/backup/presentation/screens/BackupSettingsScreen.tsx` - UI completa
- `src/modules/backup/presentation/hooks/useBackupManager.ts` - hook de estado
- `src/modules/backup/__tests__/AutoBackupService.test.ts` - tests

Features:
- Backup con etiqueta, auto-backup, 4 triggers, deteccion de cambios, monitoreo periodico (5 min)
- Backup incluye imagenes (productos y logo) como base64 en payload JSON
- Backup incluye suppliers (migracion backwards-compatible)
- Importar backup desde archivo JSON legacy (via FileImportService)
- Compartir backup via share sheet nativo
- Max 10 backups en SQLite
- BackupPayload: families, products, catalogs, profile, orders, suppliers, images

### Analytics

- `src/shared/domain/AnalyticsPort.ts` - interfaz
- `src/shared/infrastructure/SqliteAnalyticsRepository.ts` - SQLite-backed
- Tabla `analytics_events` (migration v9)
- Evento actual: `catalog_generated` (format, purpose, productCount, familyCount)

### Crash Reporting (Sentry)

- `src/shared/domain/ErrorReporter.ts` - interfaz + NoopErrorReporter
- `src/shared/infrastructure/SentryErrorReporter.ts` - lazy dynamic import
- `src/types/sentry.d.ts` - declaracion de tipos
- `@sentry/react-native` NO instalado; type declaration existe
- Inicializado en `AppRoot.tsx` via componente `SentryInit`
- Graceful fallback si Sentry no disponible

### Sharing

- `src/modules/sharing/domain/NativeShareService.ts`
- `src/modules/sharing/infrastructure/ExpoNativeShareService.ts`
- `ShareCatalogPdfUseCase.execute(catalog)` - comparte PDF de catalogo
- `ShareCatalogPdfUseCase.shareFile(uri, title, mimeType?)` - comparte archivo generico

