## APK

- Version: 3.2.2, versionCode: 22
- APK: `C:\Users\bodega 1\Desktop\CatalogClean-v3.2.2.apk` (~67 MB)
- Package: `com.anonymous.catalogclean`
- Build: `android\gradlew.bat -p android assembleRelease`
- JAVA_HOME: `.build-tools\jdk17\jdk-17.0.19+10`
- ANDROID_HOME: `.build-tools\android-sdk`

Build notas:
- `node_modules/react-native-safe-area-context/android/src/main/jni/CMakeLists.txt`
  requiere parche manual despues de `npm install`: agregar `c++_shared` a
  `target_link_libraries`.
- `namespace` en `build.gradle` alineado a `applicationId` (`com.anonymous.catalogclean`).
  Directorio Java: `android/app/src/main/java/com/anonymous/catalogclean/`.
  Antes tenia `com.catalogclean.app` como namespace, causaba icono fantasma en launcher.

